title: Eddies, Lancer clash again
text:
Greg Swiercz Eddies, Lancer clash again 
Running back Isaiah Miller is a big part of the Edwardsburg offense that will go up against Lakeshore in first-round playoff action.SBT Photo/GREG SWIERCZ Posted: Sunday, October 25, 2015 9:28 pm Eddies, Lancer clash again By Jack Walkden South Bend Tribune SouthBendTribune.com 
Edwardsburg and Lakeshore used to play annually when both were in the Lakeland Conference. 
But the Eddies and Lancers haven't met on the gridiron since 1998. Subscription Required An online service is needed to view this article in its entirety.
